                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1568</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I tried loading few fonts Angelina, PreludeFLF, Miama in PDFBox 1.7.0. I am getting Null Pointer Exception in the PDFBox, the error is given below. I used  loadTTF method.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;                String fontFile = angelina.ttf;&lt;br/&gt;
                PDFont pdffont = PDTrueTypeFont.loadTTF(doc,&lt;br/&gt;
                         Sample.class.getClassLoader().getResource(fontFile).openStream());&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ERROR &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;com.sample.SampleImpl&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; (http--100.0.0.1-8080-2) Could not load PDTrueTypeFont for angelina.ttf: java.lang.NullPointerException&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.font.PDTrueTypeFont.loadDescriptorDictionary(PDTrueTypeFont.java:354)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.font.PDTrueTypeFont.loadTTF(PDTrueTypeFont.java:171)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.font.PDTrueTypeFont.loadTTF(PDTrueTypeFont.java:154)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
